{
  "stem": "20088.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- so he tried really to provide for us in every way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What I remember as well was my brother was very much afraid of dying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was at the time 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had in this flat, there was a very small room where we had our two beds practically next to each other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was really a single room, but we put-- had-- and he talked a lot to me at night about what will happen about-- you know, if you die.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and-- he didn't want to frighten me, but he did frighten me then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went then to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we said, you know, we are very frightened of dying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we can't sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We have nightmares.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my father said, well, you will never die because whatever you do in your life, every movement, everything you say, it's-- will stay.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So you carry on living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the most carry on living is when you have a family and you have children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You will continue.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And everything you say will go into your children, and so you are just part of a chain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that-- we understood that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that helped us a lot then of being less afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this is as well part of the zeal why my father so badly wanted part of us to survive, so at least he hoped the chain would not be broken.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So we were a short period in-- with this family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was called Joke, the mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She had two little boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my mother and me didn't look Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We looked very Dutch, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was blonde with blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I wore like-- it wasn't a real uniform, but all Dutch children wore blue raincoats.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
